  "keyFeatures": [
    "Lossless & gapless audio streaming",
    "Project-based file organization with folders and version stacks",
    "Granular sharing controls (private collaborators, public links, passwords, paywalls)",
    "Embedded player widget for external websites",
    "Time-coded comments and feedback",
    "Loudness matching (LUFS) and Dolby Atmos / spatial audio support",
    "Stripe-powered paywalls for monetizing downloads and access",
    "Dropbox integration for automatic file syncing",
    "REST API with OAuth support and webhooks",
    "Native iOS app, macOS desktop app, and PWA"
